error[E034]: export fn `id` is generic; add at least one `export inst id<...>` for the FFI boundary
  --> ffi.ny:1:1
   |
  1 | export fn id<T>(x: T) -> T { return x }
   | ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
   = note: generic export templates are not linkable until monomorphized with `export inst`
